11:04:18.000Z","msg":"無論係周庭、Gphone，或者長毛、梁天琦因政治原因坐監我都好心痛，香港本來唔應該有政治犯！<br />\n並唔係好似樓主你咁狗公上身，見人後生又幾靚女就覺得坐監好慘，反而麻甩佬坐就冇所謂！你呢d叫偽善，仲係好撚肉酸果隻！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"babbd114fbd9f92c1c929e64f87e92b1e3053337","tid":2297340,"uid":39812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T11:05:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}